{
  "args": {
    "action": "store",
    "title": "Opencode Plugin API — Model Detection & Event Hook Structure",
    "category": "opencode-plugin",
    "content": "# Opencode Plugin API (v1.17.9) — Field Mapping Hasil Eksperimen\n\n## Hook Structures (actual, from live testing)\n\n### tool.execute.before / after\n- `input.tool` — nama tool (String), BUKAN `input.name`\n- `input.sessionID` — session ID\n- `input.callID` — call ID\n- `output.args` — arguments yang akan dikirim\n- `output.error` — error message (if any)\n- `output.result` — result string\n- `output.durationMs` — durasi (tidak selalu ada)\n\n### tool.definition\n- Struktur input/output berbeda, nama tool tidak selalu terdeteksi via `input.name` atau `output.name`\n\n### chat.params\n- `input.sessionID` — String\n- `input.agent` — nama agent (String, contoh: \"title\", \"agentic\", \"build\")\n- `input.model` — object Model:\n  ```typescript\n  {\n    id: string;          // contoh: \"deepseek-v4-flash-free\"\n    providerID: string;  // contoh: \"opencode\"\n    name: string;        // contoh: \"DeepSeek V4 Flash Free\"\n    family: string;      // contoh: \"deepseek-flash-free\"\n  }\n  ```\n- `input.provider` — ProviderContext\n- `input.message` — UserMessage\n- `output.temperature` — number\n- `output.topP` — number\n- `output.topK` — number\n- `output.maxOutputTokens` — number | undefined\n- `output.options` — Record<string, any> (contoh: { reasoningEffort: \"low\" })\n\n### chat.message\n- `input.sessionID` — String\n- `input.agent` — String\n- `input.model` — object Model (sama seperti chat.params)\n- `input.messageID` — String\n- `input.variant` — String\n- `output.message` — UserMessage\n- `output.parts` — Part[]\n\n### chat.headers\n- `input.sessionID` — String\n- `input.agent` — String\n- `input.model` — object Model (sama seperti chat.params)\n- `input.message` — UserMessage\n- `output.headers` — Record<string, string> (sering kosong {})\n\n### config\n- `cfg.model` — model dari config (String, contoh: \"openai/gpt-4o\")\n- `cfg.small_model` — small model dari config\n- `cfg.username` — username\n- `cfg.plugin` — array plugin\n\n### shell.env\n- `output` — object env vars (key-value)\n\n## Key Findings\n1. Tool name ada di `input.tool`, BUKAN `input.name`\n2. Model ada di `input.model.id` + `input.model.providerID`, BUKAN `output.model`\n3. `chat.params` output tidak punya field `model` — model hanya di input\n4. `chat.headers` output sering empty `{}`\n5. Banyak tool.definition events (40+) fired saat startup — ini normal\n6. Plugin path auto-discovered: `.opencode/plugins/*.ts` atau `.opencode/plugin/*.ts`\n7. File-based logging via fs.appendFileSync lebih cocok untuk CLI mode\n8. Restart opencode diperlukan setelah perubahan plugin\n\n## Cara Detect Model Per-Request (Best Practice)\n```typescript\n\"chat.params\": async (input, output) => {\n  const inp = input as Record<string, unknown>;\n  const mdl = inp.model as Record<string, unknown> | undefined;\n  const providerID = mdl?.providerID as string | undefined;\n  const modelID = mdl?.id as string | undefined;\n  \n  if (providerID && modelID) {\n    const modelStr = `${providerID}/${modelID}`;\n    // modelStr contoh: \"opencode/deepseek-v4-flash-free\"\n  }\n}\n```",
    "type": "skill"
  }
}
