    "taskId": "demo-delegate-1",
    "type": "review_request",
    "message": "Hi QA, I've completed the debounce utility. Here's the implementation:\n\n```javascript\nfunction debounce(fn, delay, options = {}) {\n  let timerId;\n  const { leading = false, trailing = true } = options;\n  \n  return function(...args) {\n    const isLeading = leading && !timerId;\n    \n    clearTimeout(timerId);\n    \n    if (isLeading) {\n      fn.apply(this, args);\n    }\n    \n    timerId = setTimeout(() => {\n      if (trailing && !isLeading) {\n        fn.apply(this, args);\n      }\n      timerId = null;\n    }, delay);\n  };\n}\n```\n\nCould you please review edge cases? Especially the leading+trailing combination."
  },
  "sessionID": "ses_105f2882affeZ2odobV8r6c2cQ"
}
